CHAPTER ______
1 AN ACT concerning
2 Health Insurance – Small Business Health Options Program (SHOP) Enrollment
3 – Effective Dates
4 FOR the purpose of altering the effective dates of enrollment in a Small Business Health
5 Options Program (SHOP) Exchange plan for individuals who enroll during certain
6 special enrollment periods; and generally relating to the Small Business Health
7 Options Program (SHOP) enrollment.
8 BY repealing and reenacting, without amendments,
9 Article – Insurance
10 Section 15–1208.1(c)
11 Annotated Code of Maryland
12 (2017 Replacement Volume and 2025 Supplement)
13 BY repealing and reenacting, with amendments,
14 Article – Insurance
15 Section 15–1208.1(f)(1)(v) and (g)
16 Annotated Code of Maryland
17 (2017 Replacement Volume and 2025 Supplement)
18 SECTION 1. BE IT ENACTED BY THE GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF MARYLAND,
19 That the Laws of Maryland read as follows:
EXPLANATION: CAPITALS INDICATE MATTER ADDED TO EXISTING LAW.
